// Windows resource script: embeds the app icon (id 1) so Explorer shows it on
// the .exe and the tray/Settings windows can LoadIcon it. Compiled by llvm-rc
// in CI and linked into ReLayoutWin via -Xlinker. Icon id 1 is also the lowest,
// so Explorer/Alt-Tab pick it as the application icon automatically.
1 ICON "relayout.ico"
